description: Despite being manufactured in 2046, the Tombolo Mk. II freighter remains one of the most popular ships in the System. Powered by a fusion reactor and outfitted with four independently pressurized cargo bays with optional external webbing, the Tombolo is about the largest ship an experienced captain could hope to operate comfortably while flying solo.
